      "text": "traditional animation pencil test drawing on warm cream paper, graphite pencil lines HB to 2B range, varied line weight with thick contour and thin interior detail, visible construction line artifacts beneath final drawing, cross-hatching in shadow areas, three hole-punch marks at bottom edge, hand-written production label in top-left corner circle, warm cream paper with visible grain texture, limited desaturated flat color fills, standing male character, front three-quarter view",
